This folder contains two archives,

vhci-1.4-binaries.zip- contains all the binaries for USB over IP implementation, its developed in Mono C#.

vhci-hcd-1.14.tar.bz2- contains all source code and drivers

For more information refer to wiki,

"http://sourceforge.net/apps/mediawiki/usb-vhci/index.php?title=Main_Page"


Note: The driver and the code is succcessfully implemented and tested in Linux kernel versions 2.6 and above . It doesnt work in currents kernel realeases version 3.0 and above.
